This project will involve multiple components:

Web Scraping: Using BeautifulSoup to scrape data.
Database: Using SQLite to store the scraped data.
Web Framework: Using Flask to create a web interface to display the data.

web_scraper_project/
│
├── app.py
├── scraper.py
├── templates/
│   └── index.html
├── requirements.txt
└── database.db

#Environment

Flask==2.0.1
requests==2.25.1
beautifulsoup4==4.9.3
sqlite3